00:28:34.840 --> 00:28:50.010
Father, if it's your foot, say, 'Foot, line up with the word of God; pain, go now.

00:28:50.010 --> 00:29:05.959
' Bones straightened, thyroid function, gallbladders, and bile ducts—function like the Lord designed us to, in Jesus' name.

00:29:14.697 --> 00:29:15.011
" I can have everything the Bible says I can have.

00:29:15.011 --> 00:29:15.902
Amen.

00:29:15.902 --> 00:29:29.279
"People have been coming up to me telling me they conceived because they prayed with me on video.

00:29:29.279 --> 00:29:35.045
Lots of babies are coming in 2025.

00:29:35.045 --> 00:29:38.760
" We're humbled to be used.

00:29:38.760 --> 00:29:46.490
Whoever thought it would be through a YouTube channel?

00:29:56.415 --> 00:29:56.640
We've come across such nice folks like Robert and Kay.

00:30:04.446 --> 00:30:05.067
