00:30:43.900 --> 00:30:44.146
We thank You, Lord, that Donald Trump is radically born again and his marriage is restored.

00:30:45.980 --> 00:30:51.491
We thank You for supernatural covering over his children.

00:30:51.491 --> 00:30:56.448
Father, we give You glory.

00:30:56.448 --> 00:31:01.628
